==歷史==
3D Slicer最初是由MIT的研究生David Gering於1998年和1999年提出的，當時3D Slicer被作為[[布萊根婦女醫院|布萊根婦女醫院]]的外科計劃實驗室與[[MIT電腦科學與人工智慧實驗室|MIT人工智慧實驗室]]之間的碩士學位論文的一部分。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Hirayasu | first1 = Y | last2 = Shenton | first2 = ME | last3 = Salisbury | first3 = DF | last4 = Dickey | first4 = CC | last5 = Fischer | first5 = IA | last6 = Mazzoni | first6 = P | last7 = Kisler | first7 = T | last8 = Arakaki | first8 = H | last9 = Kwon | first9 = JS | last10 = Anderson | first10 = JE | last11 = Yurgelun-Todd | first11 = D | last12 = Tohen | first12 = M | last13 = McCarley | first13 = RW | | title = Lower left temporal lobe MRI volumes in patients with first-episode schizophrenia compared with psychotic patients with first-episode affective disorder and normal subjects | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-psychiatry_1998-10_155_10/page/1384 | journal = The American Journal of Psychiatry | volume = 155 | issue = 10 | pages = 1384–91 | year = 1998 | pmid = 9766770 | doi = 10.1176/ajp.155.10.1384 }}</ref> 四年後，3D Slicer 2於2002年發佈，可以透過FTP伺服器免費取得，當時已有數千次的下載量。2007年，3D Slicer於版本3進行了全面的改造。而3D Slicer於2009年開始下一個主要重構，它將3D Slicer採用的GUI套件從KWWidgets轉換為[[Qt|Qt]]。採用Qt的3D Slicer 4於2011年發布。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Fedorov|last2=Beichel|last3=Kalpathy-Cramer|last4=Finet|last5=Fillion-Robin|last6=Pujol|last7=Bauer|last8=Jennings|last9=Fennessy|last10=Sonka|last11=Buatti|last12=Aylward|last13=Miller|last14=Pieper|last15=Kikinis|title=3D Slicer as an image computing platform for the Quantitative Imaging Network|journal=Magnetic Resonance Imaging|volume=30|issue=9|pages=1323–41|year=2012|pmid=22770690|doi=10.1016/j.mri.2012.05.001|pmc=3466397}}</ref>

==用戶==
3D Slicer已被用於多種臨床研究中。在[[影像導引放射治療|影像導引放射治療]]（Image Guided Radiotherapy,IGRT）的研究中，3D Slicer常被用於建立和視覺化MRI數據，這些數據在手術前和手術中均可用，並可取得用於儀器跟踪的空間坐標。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Hata | first1 = N | last2 = Piper | first2 = S | last3 = Jolesz | first3 = FA | last4 = Tempany | first4 = CM | last5 = Black | first5 = PM | last6 = Morikawa | first6 = S | last7 = Iseki | first7 = H | last8 = Hashizume | first8 = M | last9 = Kikinis | first9 = R  | title = Application of open source image guided therapy software in MR-guided therapies | journal = Medical Image Computing and Computer-assisted Intervention : MICCAI ... International Conference on Medical Image Computing and Computer-Assisted Intervention | volume = 10 | issue = Pt 1 | pages = 491–8 | year = 2007 | pmid = 18051095 | doi=10.1007/978-3-540-75757-3_60|  }}</ref> 實際上，3D Slicer在[[影像導引放射治療|影像導引放射治療]]中已經發揮了舉足輕重的作用，自1998年以來已有200多家出版物在文獻中引用了3D Slicer。<ref>For a list of publications citing Slicer usage since 1998, visit: http://www.slicer.org/publications/pages/display/?collectionid=11 {{Wayback|url=http://www.slicer.org/publications/pages/display/?collectionid=11 |date=20160329074950 }}</ref>

除了從MRI影像中生成3D模型外，3D Slicer還被用於顯示從fMRI中獲得的訊息、<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Archip | first1 = N | last2 = Clatz | first2 = O | last3 = Whalen | first3 = S | last4 = Kacher | first4 = D | last5 = Fedorov | first5 = A | last6 = Kot | first6 = A | last7 = Chrisochoides | first7 = N | last8 = Jolesz | first8 = F | last9 = Golby | first9 = A | last10 = Black | first10 = PM | last11 = Warfield | first11 = SK | title = Non-rigid alignment of pre-operative MRI, fMRI, and DT-MRI with intra-operative MRI for enhanced visualization and navigation in image-guided neurosurgery | journal = NeuroImage | volume = 35 | issue = 2 | pages = 609–24 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17289403 | doi = 10.1016/j.neuroimage.2006.11.060 | pmc=3358788}}</ref>  DTI(diffusion tractography) <ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Ziyan | first1 = U | last2 = Tuch | first2 = D | last3 = Westin | first3 = CF | title = Segmentation of thalamic nuclei from DTI using spectral clustering | journal = Medical Image Computing and Computer-assisted Intervention : MICCAI ... International Conference on Medical Image Computing and Computer-Assisted Intervention | volume = 9 | issue = Pt 2 | pages = 807–14 | year = 2006 | pmid = 17354847 | doi=10.1007/11866763_99|  }}</ref>和心電圖。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Verhey | first1 = JF | last2 = Nathan | first2 = NS | last3 = Rienhoff | first3 = O | last4 = Kikinis | first4 = R | last5 = Rakebrandt | first5 = F | last6 = D'ambra | first6 = MN | title = Finite-element-method (FEM) model generation of time-resolved 3D echocardiographic geometry data for mitral-valve volumetry | journal = BioMedical Engineering OnLine | volume = 5 | pages = 17 | year = 2006 | pmid = 16512925 | pmc = 1421418 | doi = 10.1186/1475-925X-5-17 }}</ref> 例如，3D Slicer允許DTI影像的轉換和分析。分析的結果可以與MRI，MR[[血管造影|血管造影]]和fMRI的分析結果結合。3D Slicer的其他用途包括古生物學的研究<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://openpaleo.blogspot.com/2009/03/3d-slicer-tutorial-part-vi.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-02-17 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123154523/http://openpaleo.blogspot.com/2009/03/3d-slicer-tutorial-part-vi.html }}</ref>和神經外科手術計劃。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://picasaweb.google.com/107065747472066371420 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-02-17 |archive-date=2015-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001225823/http://picasaweb.google.com/107065747472066371420 }}</ref>

==開發人員==
3D Slicer建立在VTK環境中，[[VTK|VTK]]是一種跨平台的圖形應用函式庫，已廣泛用於[[科學視覺化|科學視覺化]]和ITK（Insight Segmentation and Registration Toolkit）中，ITK是一種廣泛用於開發影像分割和[[圖像配准|圖像配准]]的框架。在3D Slicer 4中，程式的核心是使用C ++開發而成，並且可以通過Python程式使用該API ，界面使用[[Qt|Qt]]來開發，可以使用C ++或Python進行擴充。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Detection and Quantification of Small Changes in MRI Volumes|year=2014|pages=18}}</ref>

3D Slicer支援使用輕量級的XML規範包裝任何語言的CLI程式，從中自動生成[[圖形使用者介面|圖形使用者介面]]（GUI）。

對於未在3D Slicer核心程式中發佈的[[模組|模組]]，可以使用系統自動建立和分發，以便用戶從3D Slicer中進行選擇並下載。

3D Slicer在建立過程會利用[[CMake|CMake]]自動建立必備和可選的程式庫（不包括Qt）。

